	<p>Xp change for 60+ = GOOD<br />
The contraction of 60+ was bad and i fully understand and support this change.<br />
<br />
HOWEVER.<br />
<br />
We do not need to make xp go even faster in groups. Ok so before you all start throwing large objects my way think of this: HOw hard is it even for a race with xp penalty to reach level 50 nowadays with let's say 4 hours a day played (i would think most ppl who play play at least 4 hours a night) 50 was EASY and i am a troll. Boring to solo to 50? yep you bet but not hard.<br />
After 50 most would go to the planes where the xp was even better and they would ding 65 in the planes.<br />
This means that even more people with lack of skill will reach 65 and not know how to properly know how to play their class.<br />
The reason it took a while to reach 65 was that by the tiem you reached it you knew how to play your class.<br />
So xp will be nicer in other zones great but plana xp will increase by the same amount and will still be the better place for xp and thus people will all rush to the planes to level and there they will reach 65 faster and if you think that your chanter sending you a tell askign which haste is better or seeing a 56 necro asking for kei is bad then you just wait till 65's will ask you on directions on how to get to Dreadlands. Sigh<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />
Soulstorm</p>
	
	
	
