	<p>I certainly dont want group XP to be hurt, despite my argument for im 100% all groups getting more XP, it is my main source of exp so for me, that dandy. I agree solo exp should never out weigh group exp, but inturn i dont feel a soloer should be penalized either, meaning they should be close to or equal.<br />
<br />
Remember this, save 3 classes at the upper end of the game, most soloers take longer to kill a mob then a group does, so if he is making noticably less exp per mob and on top of that moving about 3-5 times as slow, that to me really sucks. Again this isnt just levle 65 im talking about here, this is across the board im talking. I have many characters of many classes and many level ranges. This is why im concerned on how they do this.<br />
<br />
I guess as it was said before and i said myself. It remains to be seen on what the numbers are before any serious concern can be valid.<br />
<br />
/me waits</p>
	
	
	
	
